Package org.yajasi.JungleJepps Description

This package contains all of the custom code to run YAJASI Jungle Jepps Desktop. The primary object within this class is the Runway object. The runway object is the transport object to hold all of the information about a given runway. It can be passed to the DatabaseConnction to be made persistent.
